comments: VanVleet (HOU) and Lofton Jr. (UTA) come together at the same spot during the loose ball and incidental contact occurs.
Green (HOU) jumps alongside George's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.

George's (UTA) off-arm makes contact with Green's (HOU) face as he jumps to contest the driving shot attempt. Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Landale (HOU) brings his left arm toward George (UTA) and marginal contact occurs as Landale releases away to roll.
Bazley (UTA) release away to pursue the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Landale's (HOU) back thereafter.
Brooks (HOU) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Brooks (HOU) legally contests Samanic's (UTA) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Thompson (HOU) deflects the ball away from Bazley (UTA) before incidental arm contact occuring in pusuit of the rebound.
Green (HOU) brings both hands forward and marginal contact occurs with Lofton Jr.'s (UTA) back as Lofton moves to set the the pick.
Lofton Jr. (UTA) establishes himself in VanVleet's (HOU) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: George's (UTA) pass goes out of bounds.
Landale (HOU) and Horton-Tucker (UTA) mutually engage and immediately disengage as they release away to pursue the rebound.
Brooks' (HOU) shot deflects off the rim and goes out of bounds.
VanVleet (HOU) reaches in and initiates contact with George (UTA) that affects his SQBR.
Brooks (HOU) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Samanic (UTA) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Green (HOU) commits a take foul on Lofton Jr. (UTA).
Green (HOU) and Samanic (UTA) mutually lock arms during the rebound.
Lofton Jr. (UTA) crosses in front of Green (HOU) and any possible illegal contact occurs after the game clock expires.
